snippet.title: Honey Sweet Lies | Gameplay Trailer !
snippet.description:
Hello, and welcome to the official gameplay trailer for my upcoming visual novel project, Honey-Sweet Lies!
Honey Sweet Lies is a psychological mystery game following Michiru Hoshikawa, a happy-go-lucky 3rd-year student who is the president of the Tea Party Club. Lately, she noticed something is wrong with her best friend Aoi, and she's determined to find out what.
------------------
official game website: https://honeysweetlies.carrd.co/
official Twitter: https://twitter.com/honeysweetlies
itch.io: https://fyshku.itch.io/
------------------
